| Builder       | Best for       | Ease of use | Free limitations      |
| ------------- | -------------- | ----------- | --------------------- |
| Wix           | All-around     | ⭐⭐⭐⭐        | Ads + Wix subdomain   |
| Square Online | Ecommerce      | ⭐⭐⭐⭐        | Transaction fees      |
| WordPress.com | Blogs          | ⭐⭐⭐         | Limited customization |
| Webflow       | Design control | ⭐⭐          | Learning curve        |
| Weebly        | Beginners      | ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐       | Outdated templates    |
| HubSpot       | Business sites | ⭐⭐⭐         | Branding + limits     |
| SITE123       | Quick sites    | ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐       | Very basic design     |

---

# 👍 My recommendation

* **Total beginner → Wix**
* **Selling stuff → Square Online**
* **Blog/content → WordPress.com**
* **Creative/designer → Webflow**

---

💡 One important thing:
All free plans usually include **ads + a branded domain** (like `yoursite.wixsite.com`). If you want a professional site, you’ll eventually need to upgrade.

